name: common-a11y-issues
title: How To Check A Web Page for Common Accessibility Issues
content:
This will be an in depth tutorial on how to check a basic webpage for common accessibility issues. Note that no web page will ever be 'Fully Accessible.'

What is a fix for one person can cause problems for others.
